latestIgtvVideos.title: How to achieve that FENTY base 🤩🧚🏾‍♀️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
AD in-depth tutorial with @fentybeauty 🤩🧚🏾‍♀️

First step hydrate your skin 💦💦 with @fentyskin Hydra Vizor 

Then I apply the Hydrating Pro Filt’r Foundation in 430 with my fingers and buff it in with the 115 Kabuki-Buff Foundation Brush.
Whilst letting my Pro Filt’r Concealer in 430 sit underneath the eyes (I like this technique because gives you more coverage) I use the Brow MVP in Black Brown to fill any gaps in my brows ✍🏾 and I’ll contour with the Match Stix Matte Skinstick in Espresso to add dimension back into my face. 
After blending out the concealer I then apply the Pro Filt’r Setting Powder in Honey where I’ve applied the concealer to lock it in place 🔐
I use Killawat Freestyle Highlighter Duo in Sangria Sunset and Trophy Wife on my cheeks 🍑✨
Last finishing touches I use the Match Stix Matte Skinstick in Espresso and Ebony as a brown liner, and apply the new #glossbombdip 👄 

 

You can currently save £5 off your favourite Fenty foundation at @bootsuk - lasts till 4th May

Available at @bootsuk #FENTYBEAUTY #FENTYSKIN #FENTYFAMILY

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#AD Self-Care Routine with @fentyskin - Valentines Edition using the new FLASH NAP instant revival eye gel-cream.
Having a dedicated day to self care has helped me incredibly this year, especially on the days that I have been feeling low. I talk a bit about my skin journey last year, and how I went through an acne break out. It definitely affected my self confidence but I learnt that’s just REAL skin.
